&lt;li&gt;Responds to emergency situations, conducts investigations and completes incident reports&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer safety audits and inspections&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit inspection reports and records daily and advise the Safety Manager of deficiencies&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitors the security camera system throughout scheduled shifts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in ensuring 24/7 security coverage of the facility&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for receiving and delivery of packages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with TMA lost and found program, and acts as the point of contact for guest retrieval of items&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
